 said, \u201cWhat is this?\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, this is a wrestler, and no one can wrestle like him!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cShall I not tell you who is even\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40245,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/29\/inform-love\/","url_meta":{"origin":21848,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Brotherhood: Tell him that he is loved for Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you loves your companion, let him go to his home and inform him that he loves him for the sake of Allah.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq li-Ibn al-Muba\u0304rak 712 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43154,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/16\/restrict-allah-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":21848,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Rahmah: How astray to restrict Allah\u2019s mercy!","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Jundub reported: A bedouin came, dismounted his camel, and tied it, then he prayed behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. Afterwards, he called out, \u201cO Allah, have mercy upon me and Muhammad and do not share Your mercy with anyone else!\u201d The Prophet said